original_title: Voyage to Himalaya - The Kangchenjunga Expedition 2022
overview: Revisiting the spectacular Himalayas on the route for ascension of Kangchenjunga Massif of 8.586m, the third highest peak of the world along with two Romanian climbers, part of an International expedition.
tagline: Mountaineering story on the third peak of the World.
title: Voyage to Himalaya - The Kangchenjunga Expedition 2022
